    "title": "Fortis Healthcare is Hiring: Consultant Physician (Principal)",
    "description": "We at Fortis Healthcare are looking for an experienced Consultant Physician based out of Kochi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Fortis Healthcare:\nFortis Healthcare is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Fortis Healthcare!",
